asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

name: Fluf n Boots
description: Meeooooow slithery slip! Oops, I mean, whats up, flufs? Sorry my lizard and cat genetics sometimes comes out first. Oh my god, like, I LOVE the underground SO MUCH!!!! Theres so many places to go, and so many different fluffs. It just rocks how, like, we all have bits and pieces from different creatures, it really just makes me feel like I now know that we all are one. You and me. Cute aye? So anyway, a little bit about me, so, my great great great grand great, great, great, oh, maybe one more, great grandfather was the famous Puss n Boots, so like, they named me after him. Im, like, really honoured. Like grandad, Im also a bit of a trickster and have LOADS of magic tricks I can play on flufs. I LOVE MAGIC! Did I tell you I can see infrared with my reptile eyes? I can tell when youre getting hot, kinda helps when I feel like breeding. LOL. Also really cool when I go clubbing cos its like super peaking on my brain with all the lights. Theres other cool things I can do with them to but I could talk for hours, so Id better stop we can chat about it another time in the underground. Thanks for the chat. Meow.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

name: LITTLE  X
description: My memory of the past is a little hazy and id rather not go back in time and relive the memories I have of the gangland wars that decimated our community and sent us into hibernation for what seems like the past 500 years. All I really remember is something waking me up and telling me to drink the "Mycelum", dazed from over 500 years of hibernation I drank the delicious, energizing syrup and now I awake to what seems like a dream. A dream where I am now one of the worlds most famous singer, songwriter and rappers with my first hit song "Old Town Road" climbing the billboard charts and taking the world by storm. My latest appearance at the 2021 Met Gala sent heads spinning and the paparazzi racing to get a glimpse at the absolute specimen I have become. Pure talent some say, I tend to agree, but there was something in that "Mycelum" that did something to me that I just cant explain. For now I will continue on this dream that feels like reality and I am looking forward to finding more of that delicious, energizing syrup that they call "Mycelum".

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)
